{"delete":"false","save":"<section class=\"blocks\"><div class=\"blocks__box\"><div class=\"blocks__inner\"><header class=\"blocks__header\"><h2 class=\"blocks__title\">構築済みのEC2にPHP環境をインストールするメモ</h2><div class=\"labels\"><a class=\"labels__link\" href=\"#\"><span class=\"labels__main labels__main--aws\">aws</span></a><a class=\"labels__link\" href=\"#\"><span class=\"labels__sub labels__sub--aws\">EC2</span></a></div></header><section class=\"blocks__text\"><div class=\"blocks__time\"><p>2019.6.29</p><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"time\" value=\"2019.6.29\"></div><div class=\"blocks__paragraph\" id=\"inputTextId-0\"><h3 class=\"blocks__title\">サーバーにSSHしてサーバーの各種設定をしていく\r\n</h3></div><div class=\"blocks__paragraph\" id=\"inputTextId-1\"><div class=\"blocks__code-preview\"><code class=\"blocks__code-preview-text\"><p>ssh -i 設定した鍵（パーミッションは400）.pem ec2-user@00.00.00(パブリックIP)</p></code></div></div><div class=\"blocks__paragraph\" id=\"inputTextId-2\"><h3 class=\"blocks__description-title\">まずは、yumをupdate</h3></div><div class=\"blocks__paragraph\" id=\"inputTextId-3\"><div class=\"blocks__code-preview\"><code class=\"blocks__code-preview-text\"><p>sudo yum update -y</p></code></div></div><div class=\"blocks__paragraph\" id=\"inputTextId-4\"><h3 class=\"blocks__description-title\">次は、サーバーの言語設定</h3></div><div class=\"blocks__paragraph\" id=\"inputTextId-5\"><div class=\"blocks__code-preview\"><code class=\"blocks__code-preview-text\"><p>sudo vim /etc/sysconfig/i18n    ←vimで設定ファイルを開く\r\nLANG=ja_JP.UTF-8   ←vimで設定ファイルをのこの部分を「ja_JP.UTF-8」に修正</p></code></div></div><div class=\"blocks__paragraph\" id=\"inputTextId-6\"><h3 class=\"blocks__description-title\">次は、時刻設定</h3></div><div class=\"blocks__paragraph\" id=\"inputTextId-7\"><div class=\"blocks__code-preview\"><code class=\"blocks__code-preview-text\"><p>sudo vim /etc/sysconfig/i18n    ←vimで設定ファイルを開く\r\nLANG=ja_JP.UTF-8   ←vimで設定ファイルをのこの部分を「ja_JP.UTF-8」に修正\r\n</p></code></div></div><div class=\"blocks__paragraph\" id=\"inputTextId-8\"><h3 class=\"blocks__description-title\">Apacheのインストール</h3></div><div class=\"blocks__paragraph\" id=\"inputTextId-9\"><div class=\"blocks__code-preview\"><code class=\"blocks__code-preview-text\"><p>sudo yum install -y httpd24</p></code></div></div><div class=\"blocks__paragraph\" id=\"inputTextId-10\"><h3 class=\"blocks__description-title\">phpのinstall</h3></div><div class=\"blocks__paragraph\" id=\"inputTextId-11\"><div class=\"blocks__code-preview\"><code class=\"blocks__code-preview-text\"><p>sudo yum install -y php70 php7-mbstring php70-pdo php70-mysqlnd</p></code></div></div><div class=\"blocks__paragraph\" id=\"inputTextId-12\"><h3 class=\"blocks__description-title\">mysqlのinstall</h3></div><div class=\"blocks__paragraph\" id=\"inputTextId-13\"><div class=\"blocks__code-preview\"><code class=\"blocks__code-preview-text\"><p>sudo yum install -y mysql</p></code></div></div><div class=\"blocks__paragraph\" id=\"inputTextId-14\"><h3 class=\"blocks__description-title\">gitのinstall</h3></div><div class=\"blocks__paragraph\" id=\"inputTextId-15\"><div class=\"blocks__code-preview\"><code class=\"blocks__code-preview-text\"><p>sudo yum install -y git</p></code></div></div><div class=\"blocks__paragraph\" id=\"inputTextId-16\"><h3 class=\"blocks__title\">Apacheの設定</h3></div><div class=\"blocks__paragraph\" id=\"inputTextId-17\"><div class=\"blocks__code-preview\"><code class=\"blocks__code-preview-text\"><p>sudo vim /etc/httpd/conf/httpd.conf ←vimで設定ファイルを開く\r\n / DirectoryIndex ←vimで検索する\r\n&lt;IfModule dir_module&gt; ←wを押下しwriteモードで編集する\r\n    DirectoryIndex index.php index.html\r\n&lt;/IfModule&gt; ← esc → :wq で保存\r\n/ServerName ←vimで検索する\r\nServerName ch-ec2-web-1 ←wを押下しwriteモードで編集する</p></code></div></div><div class=\"blocks__paragraph\" id=\"inputTextId-18\"><h3 class=\"blocks__description-title\">設定に不備がないかcheck!</h3></div><div class=\"blocks__paragraph\" id=\"inputTextId-19\"><div class=\"blocks__code-preview\"><code class=\"blocks__code-preview-text\"><p>sudo /etc/init.d/httpd configtest</p></code></div></div><div class=\"blocks__paragraph\" id=\"inputTextId-20\"><h3 class=\"blocks__description-title\">Apacheの起動!</h3></div><div class=\"blocks__paragraph\" id=\"inputTextId-21\"><div class=\"blocks__code-preview\"><code class=\"blocks__code-preview-text\"><p>sudo service httpd start</p></code></div></div><div class=\"blocks__paragraph\" id=\"inputTextId-22\"><h3 class=\"blocks__title\">PHPの設定</h3></div><div class=\"blocks__paragraph\" id=\"inputTextId-23\"><div class=\"blocks__code-preview\"><code class=\"blocks__code-preview-text\"><p>sudo vim /etc/php.ini\r\n/Dynamic ←vimで検索する\r\n/mbstring.lang ←vimで検索する\r\nmbstring.language = Japanese ←コメントアウト外す\r\nmbstring.internal_encoding = UTF-8 ←コメントアウト外してUTF-8を記述</p></code></div></div><div class=\"blocks__paragraph\" id=\"inputTextId-24\"><p>以上。</p></div></section></div></div></section>","time":"2019.6.29","title":"構築済みのEC2にPHP環境をインストールするメモ","lang":"aws","word":"EC2","selectinputId0":"h3","inputId0":"サーバーにSSHしてサーバーの各種設定をしていく\r\n","selectinputId1":"cmd","inputId1":"ssh -i 設定した鍵（パーミッションは400）.pem ec2-user@00.00.00(パブリックIP)","selectinputId2":"h4","inputId2":"まずは、yumをupdate","selectinputId3":"cmd","inputId3":"sudo yum update -y","selectinputId4":"h4","inputId4":"次は、サーバーの言語設定","selectinputId5":"cmd","inputId5":"sudo vim /etc/sysconfig/i18n    ←vimで設定ファイルを開く\r\nLANG=ja_JP.UTF-8   ←vimで設定ファイルをのこの部分を「ja_JP.UTF-8」に修正","selectinputId6":"h4","inputId6":"次は、時刻設定","selectinputId7":"cmd","inputId7":"sudo vim /etc/sysconfig/i18n    ←vimで設定ファイルを開く\r\nLANG=ja_JP.UTF-8   ←vimで設定ファイルをのこの部分を「ja_JP.UTF-8」に修正\r\n","selectinputId8":"h4","inputId8":"Apacheのインストール","selectinputId9":"cmd","inputId9":"sudo yum install -y httpd24","selectinputId10":"h4","inputId10":"phpのinstall","selectinputId11":"cmd","inputId11":"sudo yum install -y php70 php7-mbstring php70-pdo php70-mysqlnd","selectinputId12":"h4","inputId12":"mysqlのinstall","selectinputId13":"cmd","inputId13":"sudo yum install -y mysql","selectinpu